# React Standards

- React 19 with strict TypeScript — no `any` types.
- Material UI (MUI) for all UI components.
- Mobile-first responsive design using MUI breakpoints.
- Small reusable components in `src/components/`.
- Custom hooks for shared logic in `src/hooks/`.
- Pages in `src/pages/` are thin — they compose features and hooks.
- Use TanStack Query for all server state; avoid fetching in useEffect.
- Use path alias `@/` for imports from `src/`.
- No unnecessary dependencies.
